   &UR; INSTANT HOLLYWOOD STARDOM _ FOR THE PRICE OF A STEAK &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Special Attn: Travel Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   By Andrew Gumbel &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ANAHEIM, CALIF. _ What's the price of fame? At Tinseltown
Studios, it's an easy question to answer: $44.50.
</P>
<P>
   That's the cost of admission to a novel Southern California
theme park that promises to turn anyone who visits into a movie
star, at least for a couple of hours. Are you ready for your
close-up?... &QL;
