</P>
<P>
   LUXURY-DOGS (Houston) _ Deanne Doane brokers billion-dollar
deals in a high-pressure job that involves long hours and extensive
travel. And when she travels, she takes her dogs. The dogs travel
first class, of course, wear leopard-print scarves, vacation in
exotic locales, where they hobnob with celebrities, and dine in the
finest New York restaurants. Doan's dachsunds Gretta and Inga _
otherwise known as ``the girls'' _ are her family. By MELISSA
FLETCHER STOELTJE (Photo available on NYT database)
