Serpent: Biography of a Mexican God,'' by Neil Baldwin
(PublicAffairs, $37.50.), offers an elegant discussion of
Quetzalcoatl, the mythological Aztec figure who has had huge
influence on Mexican culture. By DAVID MEDINA.
