<HEADLINE>
EXCAVATING BURIED 401(K) TREASURES ON THE WEB  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Personal-Finance Editors)   (This user-friendly 975-word ``separate buy'' personal-finance
story is from ``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must
be purchased from the New York Times Syndicate's sales
