   3. ``The _____ and the Pendulum''
</P>
<P>
   4. ``The _____ Burial''
</P>
<P>
   5. ``The _____ Heart''
</P>
<P>
   6. ``The _____ in the Rue Morgue''
</P>
<P>
   7. ``The _____ Letter''
</P>
<P>
   8. ``The _____ of Arnheim''
</P>
<P>
   9. ``The _____ of Arthur Gordon Pym''
</P>
<P>
   10. ``The _____ of Julius Rodman''
</P>
<P>
   11. ``The _____ of Marie Roget''
</P>
<P>
   12. ``The _____ of the House of Usher''
</P>
