<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    POTATO CHIPS DEVOTED TO THE POPE AND OTHER VENTURES STIR DEBATE
IN MEXICO
 &HT;    EDs: Optional add begins 600 words.
 &HT;    With POPE-SKED-0121.
 &HT;    By SUSAN FERRISS 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
