   COLLEGE FOOTBALL
</P>
<P>
   FBC-RECRUIT-NOTES _ College football recruiting notebook.
(Schlabach, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   OLYMPICS
</P>
<P>
   OLY-PROBEUPDATE _ Former Atlanta Olympics chief Billy Payne,
saying ACOG people have nothing to hide, asks that if one of the
investigative bodies wishes to look at Atlanta's bid, let's do it
