Editors: MONEYBAG Correction An item in The San Francisco Chronicle's  Moneybag  column (which
moved over the wires on Monday) misstated the rule governing
mandatory withdrawals from an Individual Retirement Account.
Withdrawals must begin no later than April of the year following
the year in which the accountholder reaches age 70-1/2.
