   TRAVEL (`t' category)
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-HURRICANE-RECOVER (Guatemala) _ Hurricane Mitch spared
key tourism areas. By Larry Rohter. (Moved)
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-COSTA-RICA (Undated) _ aAn open-air perch in the jungle.
By Frances Frank Marcus. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-BRAZIL (Undated) _ Why eco-tourists are shunning Brazil.
By Diana Jean Schemo. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-GUATEMALA (Undated) _ Guatemala, on the vertical:
climbing Maya ruins and volcanoes. By Frank Bruni. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   PRACTICAL-TRAVELER (Undated) _ Stretch market for limousines. By
Betsy Wade. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-BRIEFS (Undated) _ A different look at world danger
spots; Remembering Woodrow Wilson; Britons choose plays of the
