<HEADLINE>
CLINTON AND SOCIAL SECURITY PLAN WELCOMED IN A DEMOCRATIC
STRONGHOLD
</HEADLINE>
  (Eds: See also STATEOFUNION-CLINTON, STATEOFUNION-REPUBS,
STATEOFUNION-GREENSPAN, STATEOFUNION-VOICES, STATEOFUNION-CHICAGO,
STATEOFUNION-TOBACCO) 
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(bl) 
 By JOSEPH BERGER   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
