<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-20 20:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1736 &Cx1f; tie-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CIR-TAX-SITES-2TAKES-     01-20 0743
</HEADER>
